A JavaScript snippet to convert 26 latin characters into color alphabet
("chromacons"), as inspired by the research work presented in the article by Paul
Green-Armytage: http://www.colour-journal.org/2010/5/10/10510article.htm

Load index.html into your HTML5-compliant browser to see a simple demo.

All credits, copyrights, whatsoever belong to the aforementioned
researchers.
